"Hey! you might not be a kid, but that *doesn't* mean we can't be worried about you! you lost a lot of blood!"
"YOU LOST A HAND!"
"It's *fine* I mean, Sarcio can fix it-" she remembered how Sarcio didn't managed to fix Akosua's wound "*Hopefully...*"
"Something happened to his magic."
She nodded "Yeah.... M-maybe a plasma can help, I'm sureee I'll be able to heal it, haha" *Fuck, can I really?*
"I'm sorry I got ya hurt..."
"Hey! don't apologize, it's not your fault! I was dumb enough to get close to that *twink*"
"I wanna punch him!"
She tried to stand up but she got light headed quickly
Quartz made sure Akosua stayed still "Hey, chill" She sighed "don't you think I want to punch him too?? But as much as I *hate* to admit it.... He might be too strong for us"
"We can beat him!"
She took a deep breath, and put her hand on Akosua's shoulder "Akosua, I didn't even *see* him cut my hand, he's *that* fast"
"I can be fast too! I'll beat him!"
quartz shook her head "Akosua, *no*, we can't beat him, not *alone*"
"What if I did? He doesn't have a stand!"
She sighed "He's a *plasma* too, he managed to cut my *hand*!!!! And you know I'm pretty fast, right??"
Akosua was quiet
"Exactly, he's *that* fast. in a blink of an eye, heck! he managed to cut *my* hand ***and*** Vulpe's leg!!! ***TWO IN SECONDS!!!***" She was looking a little panicked, thinking about what happened
Akosua noticed and hugged her
She sighed and hugged her back "I don't want you hurt, you know"
"I don't want you hurt either!"
"I *know* but..." she sighed, she didn't have anything to say. "Just, sorry"
She just lay there, hugging her sister. She was very visibly concerned
"let's Just... Chill for a bit"
Akosua is :(

"but we're both hurt ...and mom is worried..."
She sighed "I know, *I know*. But we gotta try and focus on the present, you know ?"
"What if other muns get hurt cause we're gone?"
She sighed "I... Don't know, honestly." *I felt like we were more of a burden than anything*
"I'm scared..."
She hugged akosua "Hey, I'm here, alright ? We'll get through this together, think about what Undyne would say !"

"Who's that?"
"Its me Rose!"

"Quartz!!! Hi!!!! I heard what happened and came to check on you.....Are you ok??? Hold on...Let me climb in...."
She waved with her missing hand "I'm fine, I'm fine ! Don't worry about it"
Shes tries to climb in but her wings cause her to get stuck. "Uh oh."

She tried to wiggle her wings out without ripping thrm
